John Howard (Australian actor) https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/John_Howard_(Australian_actor) 0 John Howard (born 22 October 1952) is an Australian stage and screen actor. Howard is best known for his appearances in the television series SeaChange, Always Greener, All Saints and Packed to the Rafters.
